{"tid":1051344,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"This Time Tomorrow - 啼笑姻緣英文版","createTime":"2019-03-07T13:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:49:05.000Z","uid":151678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac20f99766d006a0105dcb14006fb89a2e92df7","tid":1051344,"uid":151678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16VCd50N4Mg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16VCd50N4Mg&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=04697a31\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16VCd50N4Mg</a><br />\n<br />\n幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由TVB個鬼佬聶安達 (Anders Nelsson) 填詞<br />\n離題少少講，一個外國人移民嚟到香港<br />\n肯去學習同尊重我地嘅文化，連呢啲咁舊嘅歌都明白到佢嘅意思再改為英文版<br />\n呢點我相信冇咩大陸新移民媲美到<br />\n而家每日百五大家可以儲定錢走佬<br />\n做二等公民都好<br />\n唔係第時見到香港變咗中國啲三、四線城市真係永無翻身之日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d58555949a88fa7d81f06cc716d474d16d5f65c","tid":1051344,"uid":151678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}